SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
====================
1. PHP 4.0.0 or better;
2. MySQL 3.23 or better.

SCRIPT INSTALLATION:
====================
1. Unzip archive to local folder;
2. Open file 'config.htm' in text editor;
3. Enter database connection information;
	3.1. Hostname;
	3.2. Username;
	3.3. Password;
	3.4. Database;
   Do not change anything else there!
4. Enter local folder if you will not place script into root directory;
5. Launch 'phpMyAdmin' or anything else from server;
6. Open script 'doswarepay.sql' there;
7. Copy all scripts to your server via FTP;
8. Change mode (0755) for file 'config.htm';
9. Configure cron script from script 'cron/rcharge.php';
10. Open admin area and use standard username/password: admin/admin;
11. Change configuration and save it;
12. Enjoy.
